  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> Defender. You are very tough and have the exceptional ability to contain enemies in melee</p><p><strong>Power Source:</strong> Martial. You have become a master of combat through endless hours of practice, determination, and your own sheer physical toughness.</p><p><strong>Key Abilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Strength</p></li><li><p>Dexterity</p></li><li><p>Wisdom</p></li><li><p>Constitution</p></li></ul><p><strong>Armour Proficiencies:</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.GwsMGFG3ogxFrvmJ]{Cloth armor (basic clothing)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.lnYMh2YvKedWTpCt]{Leather armor}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.kVD04UqK9Yx6GeRA]{Hide armor}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.LEPCRMtCimzvXr25]{Chainmail}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.cCQ2LmmlBGYPf2KB]{Scale armor}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.7OaRnh5zUoThmChj]{Light Shield}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.bWxWgBpsJHWeTeIU]{Heavy Shield}</p></li></ul><p><strong>Weapon Proficiencies:</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.srd_rules.JournalEntry.p9xY7n4f0uabD02e.JournalEntryPage.kjW9S8gIQ0LBMF53]{Simple Melee Weapons}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.srd_rules.JournalEntry.p9xY7n4f0uabD02e.JournalEntryPage.ezGAD5rtV5TLGhDQ]{Military Melee Weapons}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.srd_rules.JournalEntry.p9xY7n4f0uabD02e.JournalEntryPage.G50MDDGV8v1NRT9u]{Simple Ranged Weapons}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.srd_rules.JournalEntry.p9xY7n4f0uabD02e.JournalEntryPage.X6ukbUgTQolHx7PO]{Military Ranged Weapons}</p></li></ul><p><strong>Bonus to Defences:</strong></p><ul><li><p>+2 Fort </p></li></ul><p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> [[15]] + Con Score</p><p><strong>Hit Points per Level Gained: </strong>[[6]]</p><p><strong>Base Healing Surges per Day: </strong>[[9]] + Con Mod</p><p><strong>Skill Training:</strong> Choose three from the following list:</p><ul><li><p>Athletics (Str)</p></li><li><p>Endurance (Con)</p></li><li><p>Healing (Wis)</p></li><li><p>Intimidate (Cha)</p></li><li><p>Streetwise (Cha)</p></li></ul><p><strong>Class Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.featuresPack.Item.7ADj4OuVS1704rgz]{Fighter Challenge}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.featuresPack.Item.IaRTeKkrO7uREL1v]{Fighter Superiority}</p></li></ul><p><strong>Choose one of the following Combat Weapon Talent:</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.featuresPack.Item.kgR65PH0ZQwSU3Lw]{Combat Weapon Talent - One Handed}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.featuresPack.Item.4OewAM0fKxcFbS8k]{Combat Weapon Talent - Two Handed}</p></li></ul>",
